Retail Price Maintenance? Socialism?<br>
Big Brother say Block of Acrylia 60pp - no sellum less!<br>
<br>
We are talking about pixel patterns in a video game. Who gets hurt if that Centi sells for 800pp instead of 1k. The guy who looted it didn't have to pay anything. The only person who this can possibly hurt is a wheeler-dealer market trader trying to buy low and sell high who finds that the item suddenly sells for less than he paid. Now while that is certainly a valid activity it is not what the game was designed for. Expecting the game code to change to support this peripheral activity is not reasonable.<br>
